---

<section id="contact" class="section">
  <p class="section-label">Contact</p>
  <h2 class="section-heading">Let's work together.</h2>
  <p class="contact-blurb">
    I'm open to new opportunities and conversations. Whether it's about AI agents,
    developer tooling, or just to say hi — reach out.
  </p>
  <div class="contact-links">
    <a href="mailto:atom@shaplabs.net" class="contact-primary">
      atom@shaplabs.net
    </a>
    <div class="contact-secondary">
      <a href="https://github.com/mrshappy0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      <span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/adam-shappy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
      <span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <a href="https://medium.com/@adam_shappy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Medium</a>
      <span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/Cresta_Adam_Shappy_Resume.pdf" target="_blank">Resume</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <p>Built with Astro. Deployed on GitHub Pages.</p>
</footer>

<style>
  .contact-blurb {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .contact-primary {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: filter 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-primary:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.15);
  }

  .contact-secondary {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  .contact-secondary a {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-secondary a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .sep {
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .site-footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }
</style>
